a35","tid":1760314,"uid":249347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:43:27.000Z","msg":"當時收費亭內並無職員，據悉附近有職員大感錯愕，「點解佢（運魚車）可以入到嚟？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348015c5f11042af5b1bbd4b5d6b1c3f3906e0d9","tid":1760314,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T07:55:30.000Z","msg":"佢點入嚟的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}